<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص١٠٧:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {فَأَنْبَتْنَا فِيهَا حَبًّا <span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> وَعِنَبًا وَقَضْبًا <span class="c2">(٢٨)</span> وَزَيْتُونًا وَنَخْلًا <span class="c2">(٢٩)</span> وَحَدَائِقَ غُلْبًا <span class="c2">(٣٠)</span> وَفَاكِهَةً وَأَبًّا <span class="c2">(٣١)</span>} <span class="c4">[عبس: ٢٧ - ٣١]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
